vents is an out-of-game coordination tool for in-game events.  This powerful web application will help guild members to maximize limited in-game time  by enabling rapid group startup via streamlined event pre-planning. GuildEvents also off-loads much of the work required to track member names, ranks, and characters across all the games they play.  <br><br>Our developers are serious online gamers who recognize the need for a web-based tool that would help guilds to:<br><br>- Keep a current guild roster by allowing members to add characters and update levels<br><br>- Plan one-time or recurring events in a streamlined manner compared to manual methods such as message boards or e-mail<br><br>- Display upcoming events to worldwide users in their local time zones<br><br>- Identify blocks of time when the greatest number of members are available for events<br><br>- Coordinate events with guild allies, while keeping RvR or PvP plans secret from enemies<br><br>- Guild News: easily post event related news items for your guild members<br><br>- Guild Voting: one vote per guild member, with results held until voting is closed. You can restrict voting based on guild rank as well<br><br>- And more...<br><br>The powerful rules-based database engine behind GuildEvents makes this possible. Sign up now for free access to GuildEvent's complete functionality during Beta. When Beta is over, there will be a nominal annual fee for full use, while portions of the functionality will remain free indefinitely. We want to create a site that is extremely useful, respectful of your privacy, and doesn't bombard you with advertising. <br><br>GuildEvents is not intended to replace your guild's primary website or discussion boards, although you may want to create a link to GuildEvents from your guild's website for the member roster.<br><br>Our Quick Tour shows you what it's like to be a logged-in user in an established guild. Check it out today!<br><br>Aelron Snowlocke<br>GuildMaster of the <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://BCK.org/">Crimson Knights [BCK]</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>Developer of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://GuildEvents.com/">GuildEvents.com</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/uaelronsnowlocke.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aelron Snowlocke</A> at: 5/21/02 2:13:36 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/urajivan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rajivan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/misc_2.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/21/02 7:49:49 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegionlinks.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GuildEvents.com</span><hr size=1> I will post this on our main website so all will see it, <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.forgottentruth.com">www.forgottentruth.com</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>If you want to do further announcements feel free to register on that site and post articles or topics in the discussion forums there.<br><br>Thanks,<br>Rajivan <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegionlinks.showNextMessage?topicID=18.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegionlinks.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=18.topic&index=1><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/addReply1.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegionlinks.emailToFriend?topicID=18.to